### ST-01: Get all airplanes
GET http://localhost:8080/airplanes

### ST-02: Submit Maintenance Event
POST http://localhost:8080/maintenance_event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "airplaneID": 14,
  "technicianID": "1",
  "eventType": "Oil Change",
  "description": "Routine checkup"
}

### ST-04: Get warranty history
GET http://localhost:8080/warranty_history/14

### ST-05: Get maintenance history
GET http://localhost:8080/maintenance_history/14

### ST-03: Submit Warranty Event
### the image is 2.8MB 2,815KB
POST http://localhost:8080/warranty_event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "airplaneID": 14,
  "technicianID": "1",
  "description": "Routine checkup",
  "imageBytes": ""
}